archimate:FlowRelationship.documentation:
Planned Orders sent to CWC. Manually uploaded by the IMT to the Arrow Fileshare where they are moved to CWC by SAP PI
Four files: • BUREAU_SPECIAL_ORDERS_yyyymmdd.xml • BUREAU_ORDERS_yyyymmdd.xml • STERLING_ORDERS_yyyymmdd.xml • ATM_ORDERS_yyyymmdd.xml
Note: This is the requested amount and may not be the actual amount delivered to Horizon.
